ars, Chalmers has also introduced the \"meta-problem of consciousness,\" which seeks to explain why we find the hard problem so puzzling in the first place, and why we are inclined to talk about it as a profound mystery.[3](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yHTiQrrUhUA), [6](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OsYUWtLQBS0)"
